{"tid":91151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"☆ 想聞下體鹹濕腥臭味　呢套面具滿足你","createTime":"2017-01-22T15:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T09:10:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0afd4a3e4639456acbbde3a4908cc3775fc41e44","tid":91151,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170119/640_f0bf8d7e4d6e887e9c9da1aa1489dcdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170119%2F640_f0bf8d7e4d6e887e9c9da1aa1489dcdd.jpg&h=c0160bd8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n虛擬實境A片是現代潮流，各家廠商紛紛爭食這塊大餅，<br />\n現在就有廠商突破傳統視覺與聽覺刺激，推出「嗅覺」面具，<br />\n讓使用者在觀賞虛擬A片時，可以聞得到鹹溼的鮑魚洨味。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，這個由Camsoda廠商研發的「Ohroma」面具，<br />\n可以搭配虛擬眼鏡使用，讓使用者在觀賞虛擬A片時，<br />\n除了能享受視覺與聽覺刺激，還能聞得到原味內褲的味道，<br />\n甚至是鮑魚味或者是洨味。這款面具售價為80英鎊(約新台幣4千元)。<br />\n（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170119/420_92cbab475eb4dfbe6270bcffe4c4d1af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170119%2F420_92cbab475eb4dfbe6270bcffe4c4d1af.jpg&h=8ed79db2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68f6b1dcdf8230158445153086effc3010200d7a","tid":91151,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要聞自己射出黎咪得囉洗撚哂咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ceee63173cde0a17a9b45e431e5100a61b219b","tid":91151,"uid":49956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset